column.Name: StyleTypeTemplateID
column.lookupquery: SELECT StyleTypeTemplateID, StyleTypeTemplateName FROM pStyleTypeTemplate ORDER BY StyleTypeTemplateName

column.Name: StyleType
column.lookupquery: SELECT StyleTypeID, StyleTypeDescription FROM pStyleType WHERE Active = 1 ORDER BY StyleTypeOrder

column.Name: Active
column.lookupquery: SELECT CustomKey, CustomKey AS CustomKeyName FROM pActive
